{{Box|text=
Install <code>{{{package}}}</code>.

'''1.''' [[Update]] the package lists.

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo apt update
}}

'''2.''' Upgrade the system.

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo apt full-upgrade
}}

'''3.''' Install the <code>{{{package}}}</code> package.

[[Install_Software#--no-install-recommends|Using <code>apt</code> command line parameter <code>--no-install-recommends</code> is in most cases optional.]]

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo apt install --no-install-recommends {{{package}}}
}}

The procedure of installing <code>{{{package}}}</code> is complete.
}}
